---
target: builder
version: 1
validations:
  - name: builder-module-exists
    type: folder_check
    path: src/builder

  - name: builder-pipeline-defined
    type: llm_judge
    rubric: |
      Verify the builder module:
      1. Builder type with injected dependencies (agent, state, parser, git, config)
      2. Build method follows the pipeline: schema validation -> load -> DAG -> build set -> build each
      3. Emits BuildStep entries with timing for each phase (resolve_deps, read_plan, build, post_build, validate)
      4. Collects steps into BuildResult with total duration
      5. Post-build phase captures git diff
      6. Resolves agent profiles per-target (CLI flag > .ic field > default)
      7. Stops on first failure
      8. Supports dry run mode
      9. Tests use mock agent and verify pipeline ordering
    severity: error
    context_files: ["src/builder/**"]

  - name: builder-tests-pass
    type: command_check
    command: cd src && uv run pytest builder/ -v
    exit_code: 0
---
